<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Delete a sub account</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"delete"} path={"/v1/account-management/time-based-accounts/{id}"}></MethodEndpoint>



Deletes a sub account by its account ID. Must be run with an API token from the main account. 
Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.
